text: Viñales is a town in Pinar del Río, Cuba. It may also refer to: ==People== *Isaac Viñales (born 1993), Spanish motorcycle racer *Maverick Viñales (born 1995), Spanish motorcycle racer *Pablo Pavón Vinales (born 1945), Mexican trade union leader *Kyle Vinales, American basketball player ==Places== *Viñales Valley, Cuba *Viñales, a village in Bembibre, Spain ==See also== *Viñals *Vinalesa, Spain
